window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After fulfilling his promise to an old friend to return to earth, Wiess and the girls return to their home on Orta. Shortly after getting home, he is paid a visit by the queen of the elf and her daughter. What starts as a life and death duel ends with Wiess and his family being whisked away to the elven nation of Straye and given a quest of utmost importance. Can Wiess overcome this new enemy that is out for his blood?</p>"; 
